In the story of YESKAY, we pursue not only the design of picture frames but also the art of carrying memories and emotions. Our journey begins with a simple belief: every photo has its unique story worth cherishing.
Let us together use YESKAY frames to forever capture beautiful moments, enhancing your living space and bringing more warmth and inspiration to each day.

product.bullet_points:
• Durable Material: YESKAY 11x14 picture frames made of MDF wood, stable structure, premium texture, and well-made quality. The HD plexiglass front also protects your treasured photos from damage and keeps them in good shape for years.
• Versatile Display: The poster frames can showcase 11x14 photos without a mat, or with a mat, they can accommodate 8x10 photos, allowing you to layer and enhance the visual appeal of your pictures. Mat opening is designed slightly smaller than photo itself in order to hold it strongly. It's not a defect.
• Easy to Use: This 11 by 14 picture frames are easy to install, Safely use turn buttons for easy opening the back and putting pictures in, without hurting fingers. They're equipped with plexiglass covered by protective film and one metal hanger for horizontal or vertical hanging.
• Stylish and Versatile: Our 11 x 14 picture frame add a touch of elegance to any room, making them ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, offices, and more. Also a great gift for birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, Christmas, Thanksgiving and just about any occasion
• Protective Packing: The gallery wall frame set is expertly packaged with the utmost care to protect your frames from being damaged during transit. If there is any problem with the photo frame being damaged, please feel free to contact us.
